This file mentioned is created by harshita jain of 4th semester section A1.
This program is suitable to run under jvm environment and uses implementation of java extensions and file packages.
The program works as under:
When operated it reads the file size and sets the file size into a given file destination and store it in the storage.
After storing it passes the feedbacks of size in timed intervals of 10 seconds(preset),hence creating log of size of file.
The log is further stored in a different file consecutively with the functioning of program
